OL,3,CCompensation claims: What to do if you
OL,4,Cthink you've been mis-sold car finance
OL,6,FBefore January 2021, some lenders
OL,7,Fallowed brokers (the person arranging
OL,8,Fthe loan, for example, a car dealer)
OL,9,Fto adjust the interest rates they
OL,10,Foffered customers for car finance.
OL,12,FITV News research has uncovered that
OL,13,Falmost 870,000 claims or initial
OL,14,Fenquiries are already underway, which
OL,15,Fexperts say could lead to billions of
OL,16,Fpounds in compensation.
