OL,3,CCompensation claims: What to do if you
OL,4,Cthink you've been mis-sold car finance
OL,6,FIf you signed a financial agreement
OL,7,Fwhen buying a car before January 2021,
OL,8,Fthere is a chance the dealership added
OL,9,F"discretionary interest rate"
OL,10,Fcommissions to your repayments to
OL,11,Fboost their earnings - and now you
OL,12,Fcould be owed compensation.
OL,14,FBut how do you know if you have been
OL,15,Faffected?
OL,17,FAs almost 870,000 people submit claims
OL,18,Ffor being overcharged, the first step
OL,19,Fin lodging your own can be to check
OL,20,Fhow likely you are to have been
OL,21,Faffected.
